==Successful Reports==

Upon successful action, on a report you had submitted previously, a notification in the "Other" tab will appear informing you.

Reports text visually changes depending on the Type of successful report, A User reports will display User, Group reports will mention "Groups". However responses received by email are omissive not informing users if it was group/user or world that was sucessful, just that it was successful.

